  "about": {
    "details": "<p>Yash Optics &amp; Lens Limited was founded in 2010 and offers a wide range of vision correction solutions.</p>\n<p>The company is engaged in the manufacture, trading, distribution, and supply of spectacle lenses/optical lenses. The company offers single-vision lenses to advanced progressive lenses, customized progressive lenses to personalized progressive lenses for professionals as well as a wide range of coatings.</p>\n<p>HOYA Lens India Private Limited has appointed the company as the exclusive distributor for the sale, marketing and distribution of \"Pentax\" brand lenses in India.</p>\n<p>The company's manufacturing facility is located in Kandivali (West), Mumbai. The company has an India-wide presence and distribution network for the domestic market.</p>\n<p>As of December 31, 2023, the company employed over 106 people.</p>"
  },
